{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_09_01_short",
  "title": "井川葵 1話 歌とダンスで生きていく (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "――ふぅ、今日のライブどうだった？\n僕としては、いい感じだったと思うんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Whew‚ how was today's live performance?\nI think it went pretty well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 7.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。いつも通り良かったよ\n最近仕事が増えたから少し心配だったけど、さすがだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. It was good as always.\nI was a bit worried you've had more work lately‚ but as expected of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になっちゃったからね\n仕事が多くなるのは分かってたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because I became BIG4.\nI knew I’d be getting more work‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 19.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "その上でコンディションを作ってるんだ\nこころや愛にも、その辺は注意するように言ってある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so I've been managing my condition with that in mind.\nI've told Kokoro and Ai to be careful about that too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 25.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "だから心配はいらないよ、{user}君",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So there's no need to worry‚ {user}-kun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "葵は本当にしっかりしているな……\n俺が高校生だった頃とは大違いだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi‚ you're really reliable…\nIt's completely different from when I was in high school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 35.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "そうかな？　自分ではよく分からないな\nそれに莉央からは仕事ばっかりするな、とか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? I’m not so sure myself.\nRio's always telling me not to just work all the time—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "学校の友達と遊んだり、学生にしか出来ないことを\n経験しろってよく言われてるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to hang out with school friends and experience things\nonly students can.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 49.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "今はこうして仕事をしてる方が楽しいんだ\nそれに、学校生活にあんまり興味ないしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But right now‚ working like this is more fun.\nBesides‚ I'm not really interested in school life.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.9941873178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "興味ないって……学校楽しくないのか？\nもしかして、友達とうまくいってないとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not interested…? Is school not fun for you?\nCould it be that you're not getting along with friends…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}